      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems from NAFEMS and internal patch tests confirm correct implementation of linear elastic hexahedral and tetrahedral elements used in the pedicle screw construct models."
    },
    {
