      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Mesh convergence study performed on the critical screw-rod interface region; three mesh refinement levels demonstrated less than 2% change in peak von Mises stress and construct stiffness, confirming discretization error is within acceptable bounds."
