      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive model appropriate for titanium alloy implant components under sub-yield ASTM F1717 loading. Geometric nonlinearity assessed and found negligible at the load levels tested. Contact formulation validated against known analytical solutions."
