      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison at the required credibility level. Traceability of specimens to manufacturing lot documented."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
