      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Validation activity replicates the ASTM F1717 test configuration used as the regulatory submission basis. Loading mode, specimen geometry, and boundary conditions are representative of the intended use scenario for non-cannulated pedicle screw constructs."
